    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I think I found out why it isn't always repoducible. In \n\nhttps://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/blob/bleed/OpenRA.Mods.Common/Traits/Sellable.cs#L46 \n\nAll the activities are cancelled before selling the building. But the animation will take some time to sell, so a new attack activity can be placed in the queue blocking the eventually sell (after the animation). I have proposed another fix in https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/pull/7544,\n"
  },
